OL,6,FThe Riddells' association with the
OL,7,FPost Office started when Mrs Riddell
OL,8,Fbought a Post Office in her hometown
OL,9,Fof East Boldon, in South Tyneside, in
OL,10,F1991.
OL,12,FFive years later, armed robbers broke
OL,13,Finto their family home in order to
OL,14,Faccess the adjacent Post Office.
OL,16,FDuring the ordeal, Mrs Riddell's
OL,17,Fmother was taken hostage, around
OL,18,F#14,000 was stolen and acid was thrown
OL,19,Fin Mrs Riddell's face. As a result of
OL,20,Fthe latter, she was left blind in her
OL,21,Fleft eye.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
