OL,16,FHe ran the Post Office until October
OL,17,F2011, at which point he experienced
OL,18,Frepeated shortfalls, and was suspended
OL,19,Ffollowing an audit. Mr Riddell later
OL,20,Fhad a nervous breakdown as a result of
OL,21,Fthose experiences.
