OL,6,FMr Riddell said: "We borrowed money,
OL,7,Fwe did everything and kept putting
OL,8,Fmoney in all the time.
OL,10,F"Every month we had to put money in
OL,11,Fand there was no explanation where it
OL,12,Fhad gone. It was just gone and that
OL,13,Fwas it.
OL,15,F"And you couldn't go back and see,
OL,16,Fwell, look at this, look at that. You
OL,17,Fcouldn't because the Post Office had
OL,18,Fall the stuff, and it was horrendous."
