OL,6,FThe Riddells are among a group of 555
OL,7,Fsub-postmasters who were part of the
OL,8,FHigh Court Bates & Others vs the Post
OL,9,FOffice group litigation.
OL,11,FThe group won their case against the
OL,12,FPost Office in December 2019, and the
OL,13,Fcourt awarded the 555 sub-postmasters
OL,14,F#56.75m in damages.
OL,16,FAfter legal costs, sub-postmasters
OL,17,Fwere left with approximately #21,000
OL,18,Feach. Many sub-postmasters have
OL,19,Fcriticised the decision to make them
OL,20,Fcover their own legal fees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
