OL,6,FIn January 2024, the government
OL,7,Fannounced that it would be offering
OL,8,Fthe option of an increased immediate
OL,9,Fsettlement of #75,000 for each member
OL,10,Fof the Group Litigation Order (GLO).
OL,12,FUnder this scheme, sub-postmasters can
OL,13,Feither accept #75,000 upfront or claim
OL,14,Fmore, depending on their individual
OL,15,Fcircumstances.
OL,17,FAs of the end of September 2024, out
OL,18,Fof 555 GLO members, 208 had been paid
OL,19,Ffull and final compensation. This
OL,20,Fscheme is run by the Department for
OL,21,FBusiness and Trade.
